158
00:31:33,100 --> 00:31:38,290
We dormed for two months
before we debuted.

159
00:31:38,290 --> 00:31:41,290
The room was older than we thought.

160
00:31:41,290 --> 00:31:46,740
We stuck foils because there were no
curtains and the walls were moldy.

161
00:31:46,740 --> 00:31:50,540
The snow melted and
it kept on leaking.

162
00:31:50,540 --> 00:31:54,500
- It was leaking from the ceiling?
- We placed a bucket all day long.

163
00:31:54,500 --> 00:31:57,670
There was a completely
broken down kitchen.

164
00:31:57,670 --> 00:31:58,980
