low pressure. Even the showers...

166
00:32:03,180 --> 00:32:07,150
- All you did was sleep?
- That place is a jungle.

167
00:32:07,150 --> 00:32:10,820
We only slept. If we need to use
the bathroom, we held it in...

168
00:32:10,820 --> 00:32:14,960
Those who need to use the bathroom
raised their hand and we go to a cafe.

169
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:21,160
We can't just use the restroom so
we buy coffee and then use it.

170
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:25,250
Our dream was not to be No. 1
but to escape the basement.

171
00:32:25,250 --> 00:32:26,770
So we gave our all...

