175
00:32:42,690 --> 00:32:50,160
I went to many auditions
and never passed at one try.

176
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:56,390
I went to auditions during vacation
from the 6th grade to the 12th grade.

177
00:32:56,390 --> 00:32:59,910
