dad removed his oxygen mask at 12:05 AM.

187
00:33:56,160 --> 00:34:08,280
When I heard that... he held on because he
didn't want her to be sad on her birthday.

188
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:13,150
For my dreams,
I don't know why I...

