and succeeded in losing weight.

446
01:11:34,080 --> 01:11:40,120
They presented a provocative stage with
sexy outfits and performance in "Poison."

447
01:12:10,270 --> 01:12:16,440
[It's a hip-hop song with a saxophone
playing throughout the song]

448
01:12:16,440 --> 01:12:19,280
[They pursued real sounds]

449
01:12:19,280 --> 01:12:25,620
[The catchy intense melody and their mature
and provocative performance stood out]

450
01:13:35,600 --> 01:13:39,270
But the provocative moves of
"Poison" became a controversy.

451
01:13:39,270 --> 01:13:43,230
They had to modify the moves
before going up on stage.

452
01:13:43,230 --> 01:13:46,800
There was an unexpected variable.

453
01:13:47,900 --> 01:13:53,170
I felt great from losing weight
so I took a picture and posted it.

454
01:13:53,170 --> 01:13:56,420
I'm not good at taking pictures.

455
01:13:56,420 --> 01:14:02,870
The next day, "Jun Hyoseong's cheeks
disappeared" came up on searches.

456
01:14:02,870 --> 01:14:07,660
There were comments such as, "I used
to love you, but I'll let you go now."

457
01:14:07,660 --> 01:14:12,140
"You're the first girl I
hated for losing weight."

458
01:14:12,140 --> 01:14:15,360
- Hate for losing weight...
- Is it wrong to lose weight?

459
01:14:15,360 --> 01:14:16,200
A mental breakdown.

460
01:14:16,200 --> 01:14:19,750
I was tormented if I had
to gain weight again.

461
01:14:19,750 --> 01:14:23,990
I didn't lose that much weight.

462
01:14:23,990 --> 01:14:26,100
Yeah, she still has those cheeks.

463
01:14:26,100 --> 01:14:29,810
- It's because I take the pictures...
- You have cheeks we can pinch?

464
01:14:29,810 --> 01:14:36,950
Because I took it from above,
it came out thinner than usual.

465
01:14:36,950 --> 01:14:43,080
Sunhwa, as a member of the same group,
are you envious of her body or what not?

466
01:14:43,080 --> 01:14:47,750
Only her upper body.
I like my lower body.

467
01:14:50,730 --> 01:14:53,310
They soon released "Talk That."

468
01:15:21,570 --> 01:15:28,530
[It's a sad melody in the minor chord with dramatic
progression in French electronic style arrangement]

469
01:15:28,530 --> 01:15:33,740
[It's been 3 years since the composer of "Magic"
worked with Shinsadong Tiger to create this]

470
01:15:33,740 --> 01:15:40,370
[A melody that brought out their singing
and the mournful lyrics stood out]

471
01:16:22,240 --> 01:16:29,070
They prepared very hard but got into
a car accident with their comeback.

472
01:16:29,070 --> 01:16:33,090
- Didn't you have seatbelts on?
- No, we didn't have them on.

473
01:16:33,090 --> 01:16:39,380
- Since they were in the backseat...
- It's the law to have seatbelts on.

474
01:16:39,380 --> 01:16:42,970
Who was injured the most?

475
01:16:42,970 --> 01:16:49,850
We thought Hana was unscathed because she
didn't say anything, but she was unconscious.

476
01:16:49,850 --> 01:16:53,610
Her eyes were open, but she
couldn't remember what happened.

477
01:16:53,610 --> 01:16:59,130
After a thorough checkup at the hospital,
she had a rib fracture and bruised lung.

478
01:16:59,130 --> 01:17:01,970
It was hard for her to breathe.

479
01:17:01,970 --> 01:17:09,690
Fortunately, nobody was seriously injured,
but it happened at the busiest time...

480
01:17:09,690 --> 01:17:12,450
- First day of comeback.
- It must've been hard.

481
01:17:12,450 --> 01:17:17,860
It happened during the first
week of our comeback.

482
01:17:17,860 --> 01:17:21,580
We were all attached to the album.

483
01:17:21,580 --> 01:17:27,270
We thought it was our chance to
plant a new image to the public.

484
01:17:27,270 --> 01:17:32,860
We prepared a lot so we were
very disappointed at first.

485
01:17:32,860 --> 01:17:41,450
But the sisterly love I felt was great.
I thought of many things as I rested.

486
01:17:41,450 --> 01:17:48,970
I thank Hyoseong who helped me
even though her leg hurt...

487
01:17:48,970 --> 01:17:52,620
And Sunwha for holding my
hand in the ambulance...

488
01:17:53,690 --> 01:18:03,410
In 2013, they released "YooHoo" from their 4th
mini-album and returned to their cute image.

489
01:18:41,240 --> 01:18:44,770
[It's an exciting synth pop dance
song with cute lyrics and melody...]

490
01:18:44,770 --> 01:18:47,980
[Describing the pounding heart when
you see your friend as a man/woman]

491
01:18:47,980 --> 01:18:53,530
[Their unique cute feel goes along
with the exciting rhythm and lyrics]

492
01:20:53,690 --> 01:21:00,000
We look forward to their Secret Time that's like
conveying the feeling of someone in love.

493
01:21:02,510 --> 01:21:07,710
T-ara returns in 2013 with a
sub-unit called T-ara N4.

494
01:21:12,260 --> 01:21:15,730
"Countryside Life" is the title track.

495
01:21:15,730 --> 01:21:21,410
T-ara showed their Korean sentiments again by
grafting Korean classical music to club music.

496
01:22:04,780 --> 01:22:07,190
[It's an exciting club dance song
leavened with hip-hop elements]

497
01:22:07,190 --> 01:22:10,150
[The lyrics are about breaking away
from the boring everyday life]

498
01:22:10,150 --> 01:22:13,860
[The motif of this song is from the main
theme of the drama "Countryside Life"]

499
01:22:13,860 --> 01:22:22,540
[Directed by Hwang Ho-joon, Korean traditional
instruments were grafted for a differentiated sound]

500
01:23:52,560 --> 01:23:56,680
Many cheered them on for
taking such a challenge.

501
01:23:56,680 --> 01:23:59,760
Even the legends of the drama
"Countryside Life" gathered.

502
01:23:59,760 --> 01:24:03,950
Choi Bool-am and Kim Soo-mi are together
again after 10 years for the music video.

503
01:24:05,040 --> 01:24:08,130
It's been 10 years since you
dressed up for "Countryside Life."

504
01:24:08,130 --> 01:24:12,620
We finished it in 2003, right?
Then it's exactly 10 years.

505
01:24:13,970 --> 01:24:18,610
Many celebrities are in it such as the
original sexy singer, Kim Wan-sun...

506
01:24:18,610 --> 01:24:20,570
Your eyes are scarier...

507
01:24:21,250 --> 01:24:23,310
Actor Jung Woon-taek...

508
01:24:24,190 --> 01:24:27,360
Baseball god, Yang Joon-hyuk...

509
01:24:27,710 --> 01:24:31,320
And Kang Minkyung of Davichi
made the music video enjoyable.

510
01:24:31,320 --> 01:24:33,970
Why don't you also give a
congratulatory message?

511
01:24:33,970 --> 01:24:36,790
- Are you in there?
- I come out a bit.

512
01:24:36,790 --> 01:24:37,690
Then I have to see it.

513
01:24:37,690 --> 01:24:41,720
After many hardships, they
dream of taking a new leap.

514
01:24:41,720 --> 01:24:49,360
But they announced another sad
parting. Areum left the group.

515
01:24:51,330 --> 01:24:59,630
Hello everyone. Even though
I didn't post much online...

516
01:24:59,630 --> 01:25:06,340
I felt much love through the
few fan meetings we had.

517
01:25:06,340 --> 01:25:13,640
I made many great memories and will
be seeing you soon as a solo artist.

518
01:25:13,640 --> 01:25:22,050
Don't forget T-ara since they'll be active
and don't forget me and look forward to it.

519
01:25:22,050 --> 01:25:24,590
Go me and T-ara!

520
01:25:24,590 --> 01:25:31,490
Areum left the group to go solo, and
T-ara returned to a six member group.

521
01:25:31,490 --> 01:25:36,330
Dani will take Areum's place
in the sub-unit T-ara N4.

522
01:25:36,330 --> 01:25:39,260
T-ara went back and forth from
the top and hardships.

523
01:25:39,260 --> 01:25:46,350
As they said, we hope to see a matured
and prudent T-ara shine on stage.

